commit.message:
Sentiment Analysis

convertJSON.py converts the reviews information into a JSON format which can be input into the sentiment analysis.
SentimentAnalysis.py goes through each hospital json file and analyses the sentiment of the 5 reviews.
HospitalRatings_sentiment.txt contains a dictionary:  {hospital name:{ google overall review, review ratings =[1, 1, 1, 1, 1], sentiment score, sentiment magnitude}}

victorian hospital reviews

Reviews for all hospitals in Victoria and Python code for pulling those reviews from the API
